overview.en: GirlX is the first female value discovery community designed for women around the world. Based on the decentralization, value traceability and other characteristics of block-chain, to achieve 'female value is linked.'
overview.zh: 全球首个专为女性打造，去中心化的女性价值发现与创造社区，基于区块链的去中心化，价值可追溯等特性，把“女性价值上链”。
